pilot jon iseminger with a laugh 
iseminger and his copilot and navigator rudolph v hobbs took 
the top individual honors at the competition held last week outside 
paris both army warrant officers are helicopter instructors based 
at fort rucker ala 
as part of the seventeam us contingent they came away with 
the united states third consecutive championship and a lesson in 
the men they could possibly face off against should the superpowers 
