finish him off in virginia buchanan said on a syndicated 
television program last week 
however tom morris a university of richmond political analyst 
said neither side can do anything to turn the event to his 
advantage particularly coleman 
but it was unfortunate for wilder because its a reminder that 
there are racial tensions in our society lurking below the surface 
and they can break through at any time he said 
